      "title": "Ten more sheds to give health oil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The government has decided to increase the number of petrol stations reserved for health workers to 84.",
        "So far there are 74 petrol stations reserved for health workers.",
        "Meanwhile, Minister of Energy Kanchana Wijesekera has instructed to distribute 6600 liters of diesel and petrol each to petrol stations."
      ],
